metadata.name: Infinity
metadata.description:
Breathing in the fresh air of freedom we discover new possibilities, feel the infinite flow of energy! Sometimes the choice of where to go next seems very distant, but every time we stand at the crossroads of worlds, it turns out that the path is always the same - to infinity of destinies!

Original painting.
Oil on canvas.
30 x 40 cm
Year: 2021

NFT: 6977 x 5228 pixels
Solovyova Anastasia
